{"type":"message","id":"14d06f41","parentId":"7a6ed535","timestamp":"2026-03-28T21:29:11.085Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"toolu_01AimJGoTbq3J5xNTzcLRMwG","toolName":"bash","content":[{"type":"text","text":"TAP version 13\n# Subtest: phase3: evaluateRules returns null when rules array is empty\nok 1 - phase3: evaluateRules returns null when rules array is empty\n  ---\n  duration_ms: 1.915959\n  type: 'test'\n  ...\n# Subtest: phase3: evaluateRules returns deny for exact deny rule match\nok 2 - phase3: evaluateRules returns deny for exact deny rule match\n  ---\n  duration_ms: 0.594917\n  type: 'test'\n  ...\n# Subtest: phase3: evaluateRules returns allow for exact allow rule match\nok 3 - phase3: evaluateRules returns allow for exact allow rule match\n  ---\n  duration_ms: 0.265542\n  type: 'test'\n  ...\n# Subtest: phase3: evaluateRules deny rules checked before allow rules (deny wins)\nok 4 - phase3: evaluateRules deny rules checked before allow rules (deny wins)\n  ---\n  duration_ms: 0.124416\n  type: 'test'\n  ...\n# Subtest: phase3: evaluateRules glob wildcard * matches zero or more chars\nok 5 - phase3: evaluateRules glob wildcard * matches zero or more chars\n  ---\n  duration_ms: 0.86875\n  type: 'test'\n  ...\n# Subtest: phase3: evaluateRules glob wildcard ? matches a single char\nok 6 - phase3: evaluateRules glob wildcard ? matches a single char\n  ---\n  duration_ms: 0.170875\n  type: 'test'\n  ...\n# Subtest: phase3: evaluateRules for bash uses command arg\nok 7 - phase3: evaluateRules for bash uses command arg\n  ---\n  duration_ms: 0.146833\n  type: 'test'\n  ...\n# Subtest: phase3: evaluateRules for edit uses file_path arg\nok 8 - phase3: evaluateRules for edit uses file_path arg\n  ---\n  duration_ms: 0.093833\n  type: 'test'\n  ...\n# Subtest: phase3: evaluateRules for write uses file_path arg\nok 9 - phase3: evaluateRules for write uses file_path arg\n  ---\n  duration_ms: 0.313666\n  type: 'test'\n  ...\n# Subtest: phase3: evalu